clear all
set more off

********************************************************************************
					*** OPEN FILE AND LOG *** 
********************************************************************************

** Set working directory
cd "C:\Users\Ken\Dropbox\Research Grant Projects\The GIVE Project\Data Management\WELI Baseline Data\Shevac Project WELI do files"

** Store project name
global projectname "weli_test"

** Open log
capture log close
